flowchart LR
    subgraph Experience["Experience Layer"]
        Users["Players, reviewers, operators"]
        Wallets["Sui wallets\nEVE Vault, Slush, others"]
        Frontend["Frontend\nReact + Vite\nmanifest-driven runtime"]
    end

    subgraph Services["Trusted Off-Chain Services"]
        Manifest["Deployment contract\n`deployments/testnet.json`\n+ synced frontend manifest"]
        Relay["Gas Relay\nallowlisted sponsored transactions"]
        Bot["Phase Bot\nSDVM phase advancement"]
    end

    subgraph Protocol["On-Chain Protocol on Sui Testnet"]
        Config["Registry, policy, rules\nfees, bonds, timers"]
        Markets["Market core\npositions, CPMM trading"]
        Resolution["Resolution, disputes, SDVM"]
        Faucet["SUFFER faucet"]
        Treasury["Treasury and fee capture"]
        Collateral["External SUFFER collateral"]
    end

    Admin["Testnet admin and emergency levers"]:::risk

    Users --> Frontend
    Wallets <--> Frontend
    Manifest --> Frontend
    Manifest --> Bot

    Frontend -->|reads protocol state| Config
    Frontend -->|reads markets and positions| Markets
    Frontend -->|reads disputes and SDVM state| Resolution
    Frontend -->|reads faucet state| Faucet

    Frontend -->|sponsored write path| Relay
    Relay -->|create, trade, claim,\ndispute, stake, vote| Markets
    Relay --> Resolution
    Relay --> Faucet

    Bot -->|advance expired phases| Resolution

    Config --> Markets
    Config --> Resolution
    Config --> Faucet

    Markets --> Treasury
    Resolution --> Treasury
    Faucet --> Collateral
    Markets --> Collateral

    Admin -. governs testnet-only controls .-> Config
    Admin -. emergency overrides .-> Resolution
    Admin -. pause and top-up .-> Faucet

    classDef risk fill:#2a1208,stroke:#dd7a1f,stroke-width:2px,color:#f6d7b8;
